---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for CordIQ - what we collect, why, and your rights."
  updated="July 20, 2026"
>
  <section>
    <h2>1. Overview</h2>
    <p>
      CordIQ ("we", "us") respects your privacy. This policy explains what data
      we handle when you use cordiq.xyz, our Discord server, or our services.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Website:</strong> our site is static and sets no tracking cookies. Our hosting provider (Netlify) may process standard server logs (IP address, user agent) to deliver the site.</li>
      <li><strong>Discord:</strong> when you join our server or open a ticket, we see your Discord username, ID and the messages you send us - as with any Discord server.</li>
      <li><strong>Projects:</strong> details you share about your server and requirements, used solely to deliver your project.</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> if you email contact@cordiq.xyz, we keep the correspondence to handle your request.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. How we use it</h2>
    <p>
      Only to communicate with you, scope and deliver projects, provide support
      and maintain hosted bots. We do not sell your data, run ads, or share your
      information with third parties except the infrastructure we need to
      operate (e.g. hosting providers), or where required by law.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Bots we build for you</h2>
    <p>
      Bots we deliver may process data of your server's members (messages,
      IDs, activity) to provide their features. Once delivered, you control that
      bot and its data; you are responsible for informing your community and
      complying with applicable rules. For bots on our managed hosting, we
      access stored data only for maintenance and support.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Retention</h2>
    <p>
      Project communications are kept for as long as needed to support you and
      meet legal obligations. You can ask us to delete your project data at any
      time, subject to records we must keep.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal
      data by contacting
      <a href="mailto:contact@cordiq.xyz" class="text-brand-300 hover:underline">contact@cordiq.xyz</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>7. Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy; the "Last updated" date above reflects the
      current version. Material changes will be announced on our Discord server.
    </p>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>
